{"title":"Muc Off launches its first drip wax, formulated for low drivetrain wear","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/muc-off-dark-energy-drip-wax","date":1773399600000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/muc-off-dark-energy-drip-wax\">Muc Off launches its first drip wax, formulated for low drivetrain wear</a></p>\n\n<p>Muc Off has launched its first drip wax formulation, adding to its already huge range of bike chain lubricants.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new Dark Energy wax is claimed by <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/clients/muc-off\">Muc Off </a>to maximise efficiency and durability, offer low drivetrain wear and to be formulated for use across road, gravel and mountain bikes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>‘Dark Energy represents the most complete balance we’ve achieved between efficiency, durability and wear. Hitting one of those metrics is difficult. Delivering all three, consistently, is significantly harder,’ says Alex Trimnell, Muc Off’s CEO.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"970\" height=\"630\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-970x630.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-970x630.webp 970w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-300x195.webp 300w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-768x499.webp 768w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-1536x998.webp 1536w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-2048x1331.webp 2048w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-750x487.webp 750w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-3-1140x741.webp 1140w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/chain-lube-wax-pros-cons\">waxed chain</a> is generally considered to offer lower friction than a lubed one, but hot waxing is a bit of a faff. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-chain-wax\">Drip wax</a> uses a liquid carrier to apply the wax to the chain. It’s a lot easier to apply, but the chain still needs to be carefully cleaned first and the chain needs to be allowed to cure and the carrier liquid to evaporate before riding. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Muc Off says it’s taken four years for its R&amp;D lab to perfect the Dark Energy wax. Over that time, it’s tested over 90 formulations, with over 10,000 hours of testing. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-970x647.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-970x646.webp 970w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-300x200.webp 300w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-768x512.webp 768w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-750x500.webp 750w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-465x310.webp 465w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-620x413.webp 620w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Dark-Energy-wax-1-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Muc Off’s testing protocol included measuring the coefficient of friction for its sample formulations, followed by extended lab running and quantification of drivetrain wear using contour interferometry to measure microscopic wear scars.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has also commissioned independent testing in Germany and the UK to validate the wax’s performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>In addition, its sponsored pros from EF Pro Cycling, Decathlon CMA CGM and other teams have ridden over 10,000km with the Dark Energy wax. Naomi Rüegg of EF Education-Oatly was using the wax when she <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/pro-cycling-news-tour-down-under-women\">won the women’s Tour Down Under</a> in January.</p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            \r\n                                    <article>\r\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-chain-wax\">\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/Silca-prewaxed-chain-150x150.webp\" alt=\"Silca prewaxed chain\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/Silca-prewaxed-chain-150x150.webp 150w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/Silca-prewaxed-chain-75x75.webp 75w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/02/Silca-prewaxed-chain-350x350.webp 350w\" />\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <h4>Best chain wax 2026: Drip, immersion and pre-waxed chain options</h4>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </a>\r\n                                    </article>\r\n                                    <article>\r\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-chain-cleaner\">\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/20250423_140600-150x150.webp\" alt=\"best chain degreasers\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/20250423_140600-150x150.webp 150w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/20250423_140600-75x75.webp 75w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/04/20250423_140600-350x350.webp 350w\" />\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <h4>Best bike chain cleaners 2026 reviewed: Degreasers and drivetrain cleaners</h4>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </a>\r\n                                    </article>\r\n                                    <article>\r\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/chain-lube-wax-pros-cons\">\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2016/10/02141025/muc-off_c3_dry_ceramic_chain_lube-e1708613248136-150x150.webp\" alt=\"bike chain having lube applied\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2016/10/02141025/muc-off_c3_dry_ceramic_chain_lube-e1708613248136-150x150.webp 150w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2016/10/02141025/muc-off_c3_dry_ceramic_chain_lube-e1708613248136-75x75.webp 75w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2016/10/02141025/muc-off_c3_dry_ceramic_chain_lube-e1708613248136-350x350.webp 350w\" />\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <h4>Chain lube vs chain wax: Pros, cons and which should you choose?</h4>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </a>\r\n                                    </article>\r\n                                    <article>\r\n                                        <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-chain-lubes\">\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <img width=\"150\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/01/Best-chain-lubes-2-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"the best bike chain lube bottles all together\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/01/Best-chain-lubes-2-150x150.jpg 150w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/01/Best-chain-lubes-2-75x75.jpg 75w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2025/01/Best-chain-lubes-2-350x350.jpg 350w\" />\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <h4>Best bike chain lube 2026 reviewed: Wet, dry and waxed-based lubricants</h4>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </a>\r\n                                    </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<h2>Plus new Chain Wax Cleaner</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-970x647.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-970x646.webp 970w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-300x200.webp 300w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-768x512.webp 768w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-1536x1024.webp 1536w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-2048x1365.webp 2048w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-750x500.webp 750w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-1140x760.webp 1140w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-465x310.webp 465w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-620x413.webp 620w, https://cdn-jupiter.metropolis.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2026/03/Muc-Off-Chain-Wax-Cleaner-1-350x233.webp 350w\" /><figcaption></figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Waxing a chain requires meticulous preparation, so Muc Off has also launched a newly formulated Chain Wax Cleaner to go with the Dark Energy wax. This is designed to remove factory grease from a new chain, as well as other oils and spent chain wax from a used chain. It can be sprayed onto the drivetrain, used with a <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-bike-chain-cleaner-tools\">chain cleaning tool </a>or sprayed via a pressure washer. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both products are PFAS and PTFE-free and biodegradable. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can buy the Dark Energy wax in a 50ml size, priced at £15 / $13 / €20 or 120ml, priced at £23 / $25 / €30. Muc Off’s Chain Wax Cleaner comes in a 500ml size and is priced at £22 / $25 / €25. </p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/muc-off-dark-energy-drip-wax\">Muc Off launches its first drip wax, formulated for low drivetrain wear</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Pnorman","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"9cc74696ae1e3b2c9679f48d030dbd1e8cfbe7a675dc390cbe013231bd978190","category":"Cycling"}